      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Cortisol reduction</strong>
        <p>Reishi modulates the hypothalamic-pituitary-adrenal (HPA) axis, reducing cortisol output during chronic stress — the hormonal driver behind sustained anxiety and sleep disruption.</p>
